text: Order Shall Prevail is the eighth studio album by American death metal band Jungle Rot, released through Victory Records on June 30, 2015. == Track listing == == Personnel == *David Matrise: Guitars/Lead Vocals *James Genenz: Bass Guitar/Backing Vocals *Geoff Bub: Lead Guitar *Joey Muha: Drums *Chris "Wisco" Djuricic: Producer *Gyula Havancsak: Artwork & Design ==References== Category:2015 albums Category:Jungle Rot albums Category:Victory Records albums
title: Order Shall Prevail
